{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"219ed98c9a","title":"关于调查川沙等三县征粮情况致陈不显电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3f697bb1fa","index":0,"year":1950,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"219ed98c9a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"b3c87df9a8","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共苏南区委1950年5月15日给毛泽东的3、4月份综合报告。报告谈到苏南各城市近期出现的物资满销、生产缩减、不少私营工商业歌业、大量工人失业的情况和采取的对策，还谈到为帮助苏南农村40多万灾民解决口粮、种子、肥料问题所采取的措施。14]黄炎培，中国民主建国会主要负责人。当时任中央人民政府委员、政务院副总理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"5b20d7b483","type":"title","text":"关于调查川沙等三县征粮情况致陈不显“电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"},{"id":"b3c87df9a8","type":"paragraph","text":"饶，转陈不显同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"},{"id":"5c098e5b78","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）删辰报告收到，谢谢你，并已转给黄炎培看，使他明了情形。（二）仍请你对川沙南汇奉贤三县情况派专人去（或你自己去）作一次调查，对于黄炎培所说因征粮引起农民无力耕种等项作一切合情况的答复。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"},{"id":"bd1edd7b57","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"},{"id":"84c0f00946","type":"paragraph","text":"五月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"},{"id":"f44650deda","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]陈不显，当时任中共苏南区委书记","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"},{"id":"faf90f5f00","type":"paragraph","text":"饶，指饶激石，当时任中共中央华东局第一书记。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a"}],"page":{"id":"7753762618","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"219ed98c9a","sta